modName: Battle-Born and Chillfurrow Farm - More Crops
summary: Adds more crops to the fields of the Battle-Born and the Chillfurrow Farm.
descriptionHtml:
Have you ever wondered how Skyrims cities can survive on what little food is produced by the farms?
Well, wonder no more! This mod adds a lot more crops to the fields of the Battle-Born Farm and theÂ Chillfurrow Farm.
There is only one downside: By installing this Mod you make Nazeem a bit richer.
I plan to release similar mods for the rest of Whiteruns farms and after that all across Skyrim. So stay tuned.
Farms already done:
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/89432?tab=description]Pelagia Farm[/url]
